window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When you go to sleep, the world doesn't rest with you.</b> </p> <p>As John's closed-door cultivation continues, Sarah decides it's time to make a name for herself. </p> <p>Her goal of sharing her knowledge of medicine comes to fruition by offering to teach a few apprentices for the Sword sect. </p> <p>Unfortunately, knowledge is sometimes best kept secret. </p> <p>For one can teach an art, but not the ethics behind it. </p> <p>Dive into the new issue of The Idle System - this time, from Sarah's perspective. You won't want to miss it. A woman's touch can be especially unique in a universe filled with planetary destruction and bloodline exterminations.</p>"; 
